## TypeScript Notes

The project currently uses relaxed TypeScript settings (`strict: false`) to work around Supabase library type compatibility issues. These can be addressed later by:
- Adding explicit type annotations to Supabase callbacks
- Using `@ts-ignore` for known library issues
- Updating to newer Supabase SDK versions when available
